According to Sky Italia, Inter Milan tried to engineer a swap deal earlier today with Everton. Morgan Schneiderlin was set to go to Inter Milan, with Marcelo Brozovic set to go to Everton.<br />
<br />
Everton turned the offer down, Schneiderlin started on the bench tonight and came on during the second half. This would of been a deal we did not expect, but, obviously, it didn&rsquo;t materialise. I feel like some Evertonians would of been happy with this too&hellip;

&quot;I don't know what Seamus' injury is but he's going for a scan tomorrow,&quot; said &quot;It's unrelated to his broken leg. It's more a muscle injury. The scan will be taken tomorrow but we are going warm weather training next week which is good, a bit of warmth a bit of sea. It helps injuries recover quicker.<br />
<br />
&quot;Eliaquim Mangala came off with a knee injury and we got a third injury to Gana (Idrissa Gueye) towards the end which doesn't seem too bad, but we coped.&quot;

